      <h2>Day 1:- Nahay Khay.</h2>
      <p>
        The first day to be celebrated on 28th October, this year and it is
        called Nahay Khay, which is observed in Shukla Paksha Chaturthi of Hindu
        month - Kartik. Women usually Vrati take a bath and not only the vrati
        women but also their families start taking satvik food. Kaddu Bhaat
        along with Chana dal is a common preparation on this day and it is
        cooked by using bronze utensils.
      </p>
